What you will need to make all of this work. Some things are optional, depending
on whether you don't care about certain modules.

  sudo apt install swig python3-pip python3-numpy python3-scipy python3-pyaudio python3-argh python3-espeak libpocketsphinx3 pocketsphinx-en-us python3-argh libpulse-dev libasound2-dev
  sudo pip3 install deepspeech pocketsphinx pyalsaaudio wikipedia
